' onclick='$.scrollTo("#toc-mobile-subtopic", 800, {offset: {top: -35}})'>Mobile tips and tricks</a></li><li><a href='#toc-mobile-tutorial' onclick='$.scrollTo("#toc-mobile-tutorial", 800, {offset: {top: -35}})'>Tutorial: HTML5 Photo Booth (iOS6/Android)</a></ul></li><li><a href='#toc-conclusion' onclick='$.scrollTo("#toc-conclusion", 800, {offset: {top: -35}})'>Conclusion</a></li><li><a href='#toc-credits' onclick='$.scrollTo("#toc-credits", 800, {offset: {top: -35}})'>Credits</a></li><li><a href='#toc-references' onclick='$.scrollTo("#toc-references", 800, {offset: {top: -35}})'>References</a></li></ul>
